passes.benefit_text:
This pass admits up to six (6) people to either Davis Farmland or Davis Mega Maze at the gate with a savings of $10 OFF per ticket.
This is a coupon pass and does not need to be returned.
&nbsp;

This pass admits 4 people to Drumlin Farm and other Mass Audubon wildlife sanctuaries for $2 per visitor over the age of 2.
This pass is a coupon and does not need to be returned to Acton Memorial Library.
This pass is provided by the Friends of the Acton Libraries.&nbsp;
